features: Power Up with Ease: This L shaped desk features 4 standard plug outlets, 2 USB ports & a 6.56ft power cord to charge your phones, laptops, printer, gaming gear and other office devices, making your life easier

LED Light Strips: Our L shaped computer desk features a beautiful multi-colour RGB LED light strip, flexibly controlled by a phone app or remote control, and you can customize any color you like via app. Plus, choose from various modes including music sync and timer functions to enhance the mood and inspire creativity while working

Organize Your Workspace: This computer desk with drawer has a spacious desktop of 66.9”L x 19.7”W for your computer, laptop, and printer, completing with a monitor stand for better sitting posture and open shelf below for storing office essentials; The file drawer with adjustable hanging bars for letter, A4 size documents, while the record player stand with 3 Cubbies open storage shelves for albums, DVD,books and file folder,keeping them organized and upright for easy access.

Sturdy & Durable: Crafted of heavy duty steel and P2 particle boards with a scratch-resistant finish that protects against daily wear and tears; 4 adjustable feet pads keep the L desk stable on the uneven ground and avoid scratching the floor; With a rustic brown embossed texture design, this brown desk can be used as writing desk, study desk but also gaming desk.

Easy Assembly: With easy-to-understand instructions & numbered parts, this computer desk with shelves can be easily assembled. Please feel free to email us if you have any problems, we will give you a quick reasonable reply

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 13, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great Looking Desk
reviews.reviewText: Easy to assemble by myself, lots if space and great look fir my office.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 19, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Took some time to put together. The LED light strips are not very sticky. Going to find something a bit more stickier for them. 1 request - have a hole put in to support 3-4 monitors. Overall great product.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 22, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Get what you pay for
reviews.reviewText: It looks and feels great. If you are buying it for the LEDs I would suggest just getting your own. They don’t stay on and a section of mine don’t work correctly showing different color than the rest of the strip. The instructions can be confusing and one section the instructions are backwards from what is actually needed to be done. Overall I am happy with my purchase just be prepared to spend several hours assembling this desk.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 11, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Deal of the Century
reviews.reviewText: This product is awesome. Instructions are intuitive and the desk literally doubled my desk space with the elevated L shaped monitor stand. The rustic color is truly classic. Desk not only looks good but is functional as well. Highly recommend.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 3, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 2.0 out of 5 stars Desk is great the power source feature not so much.
reviews.reviewText: This desk is easy to assemble and very good quality. The only bad feature is the power strip. After a few months the lighting feature that came with it did not stick I had to reinforce with other tape. Also the power brick (strip) stopped charging devices thru the USB ports. I've only had the desk since August.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 12, 2024
reviews.reviewText: We love this desk. But we don’t know what app we have to download for the led lights since we threw away the instructions on accident.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 20, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Really easy to put together
reviews.reviewText: Bought for wife for school and other projects she really enjoys it set her mood with lights haha

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 13, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Was very impressed with all the details to the integrity of the desk. Follow the directions given and it goes right together.
